des:
Are you a huge Houston sports fan? Then you need the House of Houston Flash Briefing Skill by FanSided to get the latest news, opinions and rumors on Houston sports. 

House of Houston is the Houston sports news and opinions site brought to you by the FanSided Network. House of Houston is dedicated to providing top-notch Houston sports news, views, and original content. This site also serves as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
